Yet another Milestone in the Evolution of Financial Markets!

Digital Asset, Euroclear the World Gold Council and global law firm Clifford Chance collaborated to successfully complete a pilot program to tokenize gilts, Eurobonds, and gold using blockchain technology.

The program, which took place over June and July, involved 27 market participants and used 14 Canton nodes. Five types of cross-application transactions were connected using 11 distributed applications, including six registry apps and five margin apps, with 500 transactions completed.

Following the successful US Treasuries Pilot with DTCC, the second Pilot demonstrated how blockchain technology can be applied in the EMEA market to transform the way we trade and collateralize assets. The #tokenization of gilts, Eurobonds, and gold has the potential to optimize collateral management, improve market liquidity, and increase operational efficiency.

This achievement marks a significant step forward in the evolution of financial markets, showcasing the potential of blockchain technology to drive innovation and improvement.

